hopobject.body: I'd like to apply for this job musclemeds no bull xmt india The International Monetary Fund has advised Washington to go easy, citing an "output gap" of 4.6 per cent of GDP. The Dallas Fed's measure of core inflation was 1.2 per cent in July. Growth of the M1 money supply is the slowest in two years, while growth of broad M3 has slowed to the point where it could turn negative without QE. The alleged inflation threat is a fiction of febrile imaginations.
